<item>
            <title>[TIKA-400] netCDF Tika Parser</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-400</link>
                <project id="12310631" key="TIKA">Tika</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Along with &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-399&quot; title=&quot;HDF4/5 Tika Parser&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;TIKA-399&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;TIKA-399&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, netCDF is also a widely used scientific data format. I&apos;m going to throw up a Tika parser that can deal with netCDF.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;indep. of env.&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
        <key id="12461172">TIKA-400</key>
